00:24:35,677 --> 00:24:36,734
Beetle kuning itu.
Saya nak.

233
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:39,360
Begini, kalau saya boleh
hidupkan benda itu, ia milik saya.

234
00:24:39,385 --> 00:24:41,876
Tak boleh.
Awak saja nak ambil kereta pakcik.

235
00:24:41,901 --> 00:24:43,818
Jika saya boleh
hidupkannya, saya simpan ia.

236
00:24:43,843 --> 00:24:45,564
Dan saya bekerja di
sini selama setahun.

237
00:24:45,589 --> 00:24:47,805
Saya akan gosok
minyak di lantai.

238
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:51,128
Saya akan bersih dan aturkan
kertas di tempat ini.

239
00:24:51,153 --> 00:24:54,691
Malah saya akan bersihkan
tandas pakcik yang kotor itu.

240
00:24:57,119 --> 00:24:59,411
Tolonglah.
Hari ini hari jadi saya.

241
00:24:59,874 --> 00:25:01,794
Maaf, tak boleh.

242
00:25:02,387 --> 00:25:03,982
Sebab kami tak perlukan pekerja baru.

243
00:25:04,585 --> 00:25:07,596
Ambil saja, dik.
Selamat hari jadi.

244
00:25:10,407 --> 00:25:11,707
Terima kasih.

245
00:25:13,527 --> 00:25:15,906
Terima kasih!

246
00:25:16,197 --> 00:25:17,937
Dan tandas pakcik bersih.

247
00:25:47,059 --> 00:25:49,515
Alamak, tolong hidup.

248
00:25:52,210 --> 00:25:53,911
Ayuh.

249
00:25:57,628 --> 00:25:59,099
Oh, Tuhan.

250
00:26:00,019 --> 00:26:00,755
Oh, Tuhan.

251
00:26:00,779 --> 00:26:04,257
Oh Tuhan, syukurlah!
Aku sayang Kau!

252
00:26:11,119 --> 00:26:12,970
Benda itu tak selamat dipandu.

253
00:26:13,482 --> 00:26:14,882
Ia perangkap maut.

254
00:26:18,321 --> 00:26:20,057
Tapi dia gembira.

255
00:26:43,068 --> 00:26:44,456
Nampak hebat.

256
00:27:54,734 --> 00:27:56,493
Alamak.

257
00:28:20,109 --> 00:28:22,421
Charlie, bunyi apa tadi?

258
00:28:22,446 --> 00:28:24,203
Tak ada apa. Saya okey.
Pergi tidur, okey saja.

259
00:28:24,228 --> 00:28:25,507
Apa itu?

260
00:28:25,569 --> 00:28:29,719
Kernapa kereta itu ada
dalam garaj kita?

261
00:28:30,072 --> 00:28:31,072
Kereta?

262
00:28:33,356 --> 00:28:34,656
Kereta itu...

263
00:28:35,809 --> 00:28:36,810
...ialah kereta saya.

264
00:28:37,421 --> 00:28:39,284
Pakcik Hank bagi pada saya.

265
00:28:39,574 --> 00:28:41,433
Ia boleh berjalan.

266
00:28:41,607 --> 00:28:43,307
Kereta itu tak selamat.

267
00:28:43,506 --> 00:28:46,770
Lain kali beritahu mak sebelum
kamu bawa ia balik.

268
00:28:46,905 --> 00:28:47,905
Maaf.

269
00:28:48,590 --> 00:28:51,090
Saya sedang buat sesuatu, mak.

270
00:28:51,137 --> 00:28:52,349
Okey, mak enggan ganggu kamu.

271
00:28:52,421 --> 00:28:56,502
Lain kali, beritahu mak.
ini mak kamu.

272
00:28:57,176 --> 00:29:00,227
Okey.
Selamat malam.

273
00:29:00,645 --> 00:29:03,150
Ia boleh berjalan?
- Ya, boleh.

274
00:29:03,333 --> 00:29:04,333
Bagus.

275
00:29:15,368 --> 00:29:16,881
Awak masih di dalam?

276
00:29:21,232 --> 00:29:22,232
Okey.

277
00:29:23,181 --> 00:29:24,772
Awak gementar.
Maafkan saya.

278
00:29:36,716 --> 00:29:37,383
B L A C K C A P E - M S C

279
00:30:01,659 --> 00:30:02,659
Hai.

280
00:30:15,447 --> 00:30:17,244
Adakah awak...?

281
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,214
Awak boleh bercakap?

282
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:35,842
Saya takkan cederakan awak.

283
00:31:00,927 --> 00:31:02,589
Awak faham apa saya cakap?

284
00:31:07,562 --> 00:31:09,651
Awak apa?

285
00:31:11,490 --> 00:31:13,498
Awak datang dari mana?

286
00:31:14,188 --> 00:31:15,569
Okey, tak mengapa.

287
00:31:24,661 --> 00:31:26,310
Awak suka baju saya?

288
00:31:26,850 --> 00:31:28,505
Awak peminat muzik metal?

289
00:31:29,102 --> 00:31:30,756
Tidak.

290
00:31:31,181 --> 00:31:33,366
Oh, siapa? Saya?

291
00:31:33,825 --> 00:31:35,874
Siapa saya?

292
00:31:39,774 --> 00:31:41,469
Charlie.

293
00:31:42,553 --> 00:31:45,673
Charlie Watson.
Saya 18 tahun.

294
00:31:45,815 --> 00:31:49,701
Hari ini.
Sebenarnya, ini hari jadi saya.

295
00:31:52,395 --> 00:31:54,096
Apa nama awak?

296
00:31:55,844 --> 00:31:59,191
Awak tak tahu, atau awak tak ada nama?

297
00:32:04,044 --> 00:32:06,709
Bunyi awak macam bumblebee.

298
00:32:08,463 --> 00:32:10,636
Mulai sekarang, saya akan panggil awak itu.

299
00:32:13,550 --> 00:32:15,765
Bumblebee.

300
00:32:17,075 --> 00:32:19,632
Sesuai dengan penampilan awak.

301
00:32:45,844 --> 00:32:47,777
Aku nak bercerai, Roy!
- Jangan begitu, Amber.

302
00:32:47,802 --> 00:32:49,574
Beri aku alasan yang baik.

303
00:32:49,599 --> 00:32:51,310
Kau cuba tiduri adik aku!

304
00:32:51,370 --> 00:32:52,974
Aku tak berjaya!

305
00:32:52,999 --> 00:32:54,763
Ya, segala yang kau buat tak berjaya.

306
00:32:54,788 --> 00:32:57,889
Biaya pendahuluan itu ialah untuk rumah.
Kau beli kereta.

307
00:32:57,914 --> 00:33:00,969
Kau bodoh ke, Roy?
Kita tak perlukan kereta.

308
00:33:01,017 --> 00:33:03,650
Bertenang dan dengar cakap aku.

309
00:33:06,979 --> 00:33:09,641
Apa itu?
- Apa?

310
00:33:13,271 --> 00:33:15,229
Alamak, Roy.
Benda itu menuju ke arah kita!

311
00:33:15,659 --> 00:33:17,043
Tidak!

312
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:19,239
Jangan terkena kereta aku.

313
00:33:19,504 --> 00:33:20,818
Tolong, jangan kena kereta aku!

314
00:33:32,225 --> 00:33:33,948
Ya, syukurlah, kereta aku!

315
00:33:34,893 --> 00:33:36,187
Ya, aku okey.

316
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:38,952
Baguslah, sayang.

317
00:33:40,556 --> 00:33:42,156
Lari!

318
00:34:01,428 --> 00:34:02,690
Itu kereta aku ke?

319
00:34:05,752 --> 00:34:06,752
Helo...

320
00:34:21,384 --> 00:34:22,384
Alamak!

321
00:34:22,650 --> 00:34:23,650
Bumi.

322
00:34:24,822 --> 00:34:27,217
Langsung tak mengujakan.

323
00:34:27,624 --> 00:34:30,474
Hidupan peribumi di sini lebih primitif
dari yang aku jangka.

324
00:34:37,575 --> 00:34:38,975
Aku suka cara mereka meletup.

325
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:40,746
Fokus, komrad.

326
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:45,938
Isyarat kecemasan B-127 datang
dari pantai barat benua ini.

327
00:34:46,125 --> 00:34:48,951
Buat masa ini, kita ke barat.

328
00:35:03,389 --> 00:35:05,430
Bila lagi mereka nak ajar
awak guna <i>nunchuck</i>?

329
00:35:05,455 --> 00:35:06,962
Entahlah.
Saya harap tak lama lagi.

330
00:35:07,092 --> 00:35:08,470
Pagi! Jumpa lagi.

331
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:10,229
Kamu tergesa-gesa nak ke mana?

332
00:35:10,325 --> 00:35:11,325
Tak ke mana.

333
00:35:11,739 --> 00:35:12,739
Jumpa lagi.

334
00:35:14,594 --> 00:35:16,294
Pagi, Bum...

335
00:35:18,658 --> 00:35:19,659
Bee?

336
00:35:21,902 --> 00:35:23,702
Bee, mana awak?

337
00:35:27,114 --> 00:35:28,914
Alamak.

338
00:35:29,052 --> 00:35:30,966
Bee!

339
00:35:31,216 --> 00:35:32,216
Mana awak pergi?

340
00:35:38,565 --> 00:35:39,566
Otis!

341
00:35:40,837 --> 00:35:42,093
Kamu nampak tak kereta kakak?

342
00:35:42,636 --> 00:35:43,636
Malangnya, ya.

343
00:35:43,709 --> 00:35:45,812
Tak, kamu nampak kereta kakak hari ini?

344
00:35:46,084 --> 00:35:47,814
Ia di dalam garaj.
Ada orang curi ia!

345
00:35:48,139 --> 00:35:49,528
Tak, dungu.
Mak pandu ia.

346
00:35:50,060 --> 00:35:53,271
Mak bawa Conan jumpa doktor haiwan
sebab ia tertelan sarung tangan getah.

347
00:35:53,469 --> 00:35:54,469
Dan Ron perlu pakai <i>Station Wagon</i> itu.

348
00:35:54,765 --> 00:35:55,766
Syukurlah.

349
00:35:58,768 --> 00:36:00,164
Kejap.

350
00:36:05,461 --> 00:36:07,782
Maaf, ini saya sekali lagi.

351
00:36:08,009 --> 00:36:09,897
Kita belum berkenalan, tapi...
- Saya sibuk sekarang, maaf.

352
00:36:10,162 --> 00:36:11,162
Tidak. Ya.

353
00:36:11,815 --> 00:36:12,815
Okey.

354
00:36:15,895 --> 00:36:18,628
Mak tahu.
Bertahan dulu.

355
00:36:21,132 --> 00:36:23,293
Kamu tak boleh makan
segala yang kamu nampak.

356
00:36:23,765 --> 00:36:26,166
Jadikan ini satu iktibar.

357
00:36:28,183 --> 00:36:31,076
Hentikan!
Jangan buat begitu!

358
00:36:35,986 --> 00:36:36,986
Bee, jangan!

359
00:36:42,155 --> 00:36:43,155
Mak!

360
00:36:44,756 --> 00:36:46,829
Charlie, apa kamu buat?

361
00:36:46,971 --> 00:36:47,971
Mak, berhenti.

362
00:36:48,245 --> 00:36:49,245
Apa berlaku?

363
00:36:49,651 --> 00:36:51,251
Cepat berhenti.

364
00:36:51,733 --> 00:36:54,033
Okey, baik.

365
00:36:57,099 --> 00:37:00,858
Tolong simpan kemaluan robot awak.
Awak gila ke?

366
00:37:01,137 --> 00:37:03,878
Mak hampir diserang sakit jantung.
Mak ingat ada orang nak samun kereta.

367
00:37:03,903 --> 00:37:05,569
Mak nak bawa anjing ini
jumpa doktor haiwan.

368
00:37:05,585 --> 00:37:07,666
Tak sangka mak akan bawa dia tanpa saya.

369
00:37:07,905 --> 00:37:09,424
Mak, saya risaukan dia!

370
00:37:09,542 --> 00:37:11,148
Dia pun anjing saya juga!

371
00:37:11,525 --> 00:37:13,706
Kamu kata Conan anjing Otis.

372
00:37:14,391 --> 00:37:15,824
Jangan mengarut, mak.

373
00:37:15,969 --> 00:37:17,639
Mak tak boleh memandu
dalam keadaan stres.

374
00:37:17,664 --> 00:37:19,683
Saya tahu macam mana perangai
mak ketika kecemasan.

375
00:37:20,525 --> 00:37:21,925
Mak seorang jururawat.

376
00:37:23,753 --> 00:37:24,754
Bukan untuk haiwan.

377
00:37:30,733 --> 00:37:32,567
Okey.
Kalau kamu nak memandu. Sila.

378
00:37:33,332 --> 00:37:35,786
Lagipun, kamu tak pakai helmet.
Mak tak nampak ia.

379
00:37:39,882 --> 00:37:40,882
Jangan buat hal, Bee.

380
00:37:48,874 --> 00:37:49,875
Tuan?

381
00:37:51,161 --> 00:37:54,311
Tuan mesti tengok ini segera.

382
00:37:59,605 --> 00:38:00,713
Kau pasti?

383
00:38:00,784 --> 00:38:02,979
Ya, tuan.
Dia dari mereka baru tiba di Texas.

384
00:38:03,508 --> 00:38:05,486
Menurut maklumat, mereka menuju ke barat.

385
00:38:05,798 --> 00:38:07,699
Bersiap sedia, Simmons.

386
00:38:07,830 --> 00:38:09,631
Kita akan pergi ke Texas.

387
00:38:11,798 --> 00:38:14,416
Okey, Bee.
Saya nak jelaskan sedikit benda.

388
00:38:20,136 --> 00:38:21,825
Okey, kita selamat.

389
00:38:24,737 --> 00:38:25,737
Baiklah.

390
00:38:25,884 --> 00:38:27,832
Lain kali bukan di pantai.

391
00:38:29,782 --> 00:38:31,255
Oh, saya okey.

392
00:38:32,629 --> 00:38:34,296
Saya okey.
Terima kasih.

393
00:38:35,540 --> 00:38:39,457
Orang akan buat benda buruk pada
benda yang mereka tak faham.

394
00:38:39,604 --> 00:38:44,061
Jika mereka nampak awak, mereka akan kunci
awak dalam makmal atau leraikan awak.

395
00:38:44,499 --> 00:38:47,220
Ia teruk.
Percayalah.

396
00:38:50,581 --> 00:38:54,373
Awak cuma tonjolkan diri
awak kepada saya, okey?

397
00:38:56,076 --> 00:38:58,473
Mari kita berlatih.
Awak dah sedia?

398
00:38:58,709 --> 00:39:01,303
Jika awak nampak orang lain,
selain saya, apa awak buat?

399
00:39:03,373 --> 00:39:05,469
Bagus.

400
00:39:05,632 --> 00:39:06,629
Keluar sekarang.

401
00:39:08,623 --> 00:39:11,301
Okey, andai kata kita tengah
memandu dan tiba-tiba...

402
00:39:11,312 --> 00:39:13,913
Alamak! Ada orang datang!
Sembunyi, Bee!

403
00:39:26,251 --> 00:39:27,751
Biar betul?

404
00:39:31,964 --> 00:39:33,786
Bee, dah terlambat.
Awak dah mati.

405
00:39:38,348 --> 00:39:41,100
Tak mengapa.
Sebab itu kita berlatih.

406
00:39:41,973 --> 00:39:42,973
Nanti awak akan faham.

407
00:39:44,191 --> 00:39:48,256
<i>Fox-2 datang.
Pendatang bukan manusia sedang ke mari.</i>

408
00:40:04,838 --> 00:40:08,022
Matlamat kita, tuan,
ialah berkomunikasi dengan mereka.

409
00:40:08,087 --> 00:40:11,328
Pertemuan pertama
dengan spesies alien.

410
00:40:12,018 --> 00:40:14,805
Seumur hidup aku menunggu saat ini.

411
00:40:14,830 --> 00:40:18,012
Jika mereka cuba apa-apa,
kita hapuskan mereka.

412
00:40:34,037 --> 00:40:36,762
Bilangan manusia semakin ramai.
Izinkan aku bunuh mereka.

413
00:40:36,787 --> 00:40:37,286
Belum lagi.

414
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:41,053
Isyarat B-127 telah hilang.

415
00:40:41,191 --> 00:40:43,391
Aku ada idea.

416
00:40:44,326 --> 00:40:48,054
Dengar sini!
Aku Ejen Burns dan ini Dr. Powell.

417
00:40:48,079 --> 00:40:51,781
Ketika ini 100 pucuk senjata
sedang dituding ke arah kau.

418
00:40:51,806 --> 00:40:53,828
Jadi, nyatakan urusan kau.

419
00:40:53,887 --> 00:41:00,027
Penghuni Bumi, kami pasukan pengaman
Decepticon yang meronda galaksi.

420
00:41:00,060 --> 00:41:03,494
Apa kau buat?
Ini memalukan.

421
00:41:03,583 --> 00:41:07,460
Kami percaya penjenayah
bahaya dari dunia kami...

422
00:41:07,485 --> 00:41:10,431
...sedang bersembunyi
di planet awak.

423
00:41:10,499 --> 00:41:12,173
Bagaimana kami boleh bantu?

424
00:41:13,675 --> 00:41:15,940
Kami perlukan alat pemantauan awak.

425
00:41:16,334 --> 00:41:19,722
Kejap.
Kau nak guna akses kepada satelit kami?

426
00:41:19,907 --> 00:41:22,167
Jarak pengimbas kami terhad.

427
00:41:23,397 --> 00:41:26,292
Infrastruktur awak primitif.

428
00:41:26,509 --> 00:41:29,790
Tapi jika digandingkan, ia amat berkesan.

429
00:41:29,837 --> 00:41:31,602
Mustahil. Tak boleh.

430
00:41:31,856 --> 00:41:34,396
Kita memiliki musuh
yang sama, Ejen Barnes.

431
00:41:34,765 --> 00:41:37,007
Ada perang sedang
melanda planet kami.

432
00:41:37,631 --> 00:41:41,731
Jika B-127 tak ditemui,
perang itu akan menular ke sini.

433
00:41:42,102 --> 00:41:46,121
Mungkin kita boleh cari jalan
untuk saling membantu.

434
00:41:47,088 --> 00:41:49,982
Kami akan berbincang
dengan pegawai atasan kami.

435
00:41:50,007 --> 00:41:51,010
Sementara itu...

436
00:41:51,469 --> 00:41:52,547
...ikut kami.

437
00:41:52,569 --> 00:41:54,676
Baiklah, saudara Powell.

438
00:41:54,981 --> 00:41:57,167
Bawa kami berjumpa pemimpin awak.

439
00:42:07,655 --> 00:42:10,265
Tentu teruk kan terperuk dalam
VW sepanjang hari.

440
00:42:11,756 --> 00:42:13,735
Ada sesiapa boleh bantu awak?

441
00:42:14,330 --> 00:42:15,330
Awak ada keluarga?

442
00:42:16,665 --> 00:42:19,165
Contohnya mak, ayah, adik beradik?

443
00:42:19,221 --> 00:42:20,521
Awak sayangkan satu sama lain?

444
00:42:23,072 --> 00:42:27,698
Atau saling membenci dan tak sabar
nak lari dan mulakan kehidupan baru.

445
00:42:33,340 --> 00:42:35,434
Awak nak tahu jika saya boleh baikinya?

446
00:42:37,316 --> 00:42:39,457
Saya akan hati-hati.
Saya janji.

447
00:42:53,649 --> 00:42:54,649
Boleh baring tak?

448
00:42:58,897 --> 00:42:59,897
Jangan bergerak.

449
00:43:03,436 --> 00:43:05,173
Mungkin ada sesuatu...

450
00:43:16,479 --> 00:43:18,079
<i>B-127...</i>

451
00:43:19,330 --> 00:43:22,348
<i>...saya doakan awak menerima mesej ini.</i>

452
00:43:22,883 --> 00:43:24,984
<i>Perang kita terus melanda.</i>

453
00:43:25,312 --> 00:43:27,112
<i>...Planet Bumi...</i>

454
00:43:27,884 --> 00:43:29,685
<i>...keselamatan kita...</i>

455
00:43:55,072 --> 00:43:57,072
Ravage, lenting!

456
00:44:14,482 --> 00:44:16,218
<i>...misi awak...</i>

457
00:44:16,726 --> 00:44:17,726
<i>...askar...</i>

458
00:44:18,137 --> 00:44:19,137
<i>...saya...</i>

459
00:44:23,052 --> 00:44:24,610
Awak okey?

460
00:44:27,576 --> 00:44:28,577
Siapa dia?

461
00:44:29,937 --> 00:44:32,814
Suara itu berkata sesuatu pasal perang?

462
00:44:33,743 --> 00:44:35,443
Awak ingat apa-apa?

463
00:44:38,922 --> 00:44:42,798
Adakah Beetle VW satu penyamaran?

464
00:44:43,431 --> 00:44:45,638
Awak sembunyikan sesuatu?

465
00:44:49,420 --> 00:44:50,420
Awak takut?

