745
01:11:36,418 --> 01:11:38,118
Sayang, jangan sentuh rambut mak.

746
01:11:42,670 --> 01:11:46,558
Pergi, sekarang.
Senyap-senyap.

747
01:11:46,847 --> 01:11:47,847
Mak, kejap!

748
01:11:50,039 --> 01:11:51,040
Alamak!

749
01:11:53,686 --> 01:11:56,210
Mak.
- Apa berlaku?

750
01:11:56,889 --> 01:11:58,434
Mak, maaf. Ini semua salah saya.

751
01:11:58,459 --> 01:12:00,196
Apa kakak dah
buat pada TV saya?

752
