tak perlu layan karenah saya lagi!

767
01:12:51,246 --> 01:12:52,246
Charlie!

768
01:13:02,580 --> 01:13:03,580
Awak okey?

769
01:13:05,296 --> 01:13:07,013
Ya.

770
